<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Reset Your Password</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      overflow: hidden;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: rgb(61, 34, 24);
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px 20px;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .content h2 {
      color: rgb(61, 34, 24);
      margin-top: 0;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      background-color: #9b6c43;
      color: #fff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }
    .button:hover {
      background-color: #81573a;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #999;
      margin-top: 30px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #999;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .container {
        margin: 20px;
        padding: 15px;
      }
      .header {
        font-size: 20px;
        padding: 20px 15px;
      }
      .button {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 14px 0;
        text-align: center;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      Tasteorama
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Reset Your Password</h2>
      <p>Hello!</p>
      <p>We received a request to reset the password for your Tasteorama account.</p>
      <p>To reset your password you have 15 minutes, please click the button below:</p>
      <p style="text-align:center;">
        <a href="{{resetPasswordLink}}" class="button">Reset Password</a>
      </p>
      <p>If the button doesnâ€™t work, copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
      <p style="word-break: break-all;">{{resetPasswordLink}}</p>
      <p>If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email. Your password will remain unchanged.</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br>The Tasteorama Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; 2025 Tasteorama. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>